descriptionHTML:
Esque is a free Facepak that will bring weather information to your wrist in a nice Material Design look. See the Temperature, Humidity, Precipitation and the High/Lows at a quick glance. The weather icon and stats change every hour.

*Custom background support
*Custom hue support

*YOU MUST HAVE THE APP "FACE" TO USE THIS FACE
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=boxcrab.face
